  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy for TapTacToe</h1>

    <p class="date">Effective Date: 16 June 2026</p>

    <p>
      TapTacToe is a Tic Tac Toe game application developed by Meet ghori.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      TapTacToe does not collect, store, share, or transmit any personal information from users.
    </p>
    <p>
      The app does not require user registration, login, email address, phone number, location,
      contacts, photos, camera, microphone, or any other personal data.
    </p>

    <h2>How the App Works</h2>
    <p>
      TapTacToe works locally on the user's device. Game actions such as selecting grid size,
      choosing game mode, playing with a friend, playing with the robot, and resetting the game
      are handled inside the app only.
    </p>
    <p>
      No gameplay data is uploaded to any server.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services and SDKs</h2>
    <p>
      The app uses Android SDK, Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, AndroidX Lifecycle ViewModel,
      Material Icons, Material 3, and Accompanist System UI Controller for app functionality
      and user interface.
    </p>
    <p>
      These libraries are used only to build and run the app interface and game logic.
      They are not used to collect personal user data.
    </p>

    <h2>Advertising and Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      TapTacToe does not use advertising SDKs, analytics SDKs, tracking SDKs, or third-party
      data collection tools.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      TapTacToe does not knowingly collect personal information from children or any other users.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      Since TapTacToe does not collect user data, no user data is shared with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any updates will be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
